REQUIREMENTS

  SDL-1.2.x       -- http://libsdl.org
  sdl-ada         -- http://coreland.ath.cx/git/sdl-ada.git/  (git repository)
                     http://coreland.ath.cx/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=sdl-ada.git
  agar-core-ada   -- http://libagar.org/
                     http://coreland.ath.cx/git/agar-ada.git/ (git repository)
                     http://coreland.ath.cx/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=agar-ada.git
  agar-gui-ada    -- http://libagar.org/
                     http://coreland.ath.cx/git/agar-gui-ada.git/ (git repository)
                     http://coreland.ath.cx/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=agar-gui-ada.git

COMPILATION EXAMPLE

  $ make
